{"questionId":"14590979","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Daniela wins a prize. She is offered two options for receiving her winnings over a period of three years.</p>\n<p>Option A: Daniela receives $5500 at the end of each month.</p>\n<p>Option B: Daniela receives $2000 at the end of the first month. Each month after this, the amount she receives increases by 6%.</p></div>\n<p>Option A;</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>5500</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>36</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mfenced><mo>$</mo></mfenced><mn>198000</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right;\"><em><strong>[2 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"14590979","referenceCode":"23N.2.SL.TZ2.8ai","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"Option A;","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.3—Geometric sequences and series"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":3}
